{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"95607b0f5b","title":"抚易白沙烈士联","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"dd1d320c31","index":0,"year":1921,"month":8,"day":null,"articleId":"95607b0f5b"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji2","name":"毛泽东全集第2卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji2.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji2":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"9ec02e9d05","type":"paragraph","text":"抚易白沙烈士联","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji2","articleId":"95607b0f5b"},{"id":"27f90b377c","type":"paragraph","text":"（1921年8月）无用之人不死，有用之人惯死则，我为民国前途哭；去年追快杨公，今年追惊易公，其奈长沙后进何叫[1]易白沙（1886-1921），名坤，字越村，湖南长沙人，家居白沙异附近，反清烈士易培基之弟。1921年5月问，他只身赴北京，准各何机刺杀北洋军阀政府首脑，但未成功。于是又乘海轮至广州遇见孙中山，请求组织军队北线。由于广东形势未稳，亦未如愿。激情之下，于农历五月初五晚来到明代大衡陈白沙（1428-1500）故里新会县陈村海边海，以死摄国，年仅35岁。毛泽东书此换联。2赞死，悲而死。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji2","articleId":"95607b0f5b"}],"page":{"id":"f3cc0548d0","publicationId":"maoquanji2","articleId":"95607b0f5b","start":446,"end":446}}}},"__N_SSG":true}